The neighbors are: 2025 (bottom), 2027 (right), 2024 (top), 2023 (top-left), 2028 (right-bottom), 2029 (right-top), 2022 (left-top), and 2020 (left-bottom). The sum of these numbers will give us the desired result.

## Step 9: Perform the sum
